main event: A UFO was sighted near McClellan Air Force Base, California on December 26, 1966.
interesting points: The sighting involved a bright object that displayed unusual speed and maneuverability,The object was described as orange and disappeared quickly from view, There were multiple reports from witnesses including military personnel and civilians, No physical evidence was found to support the sighting, The conclusions of the reports indicated insufficient data for evaluation.
witness description: Military personnel and civilians; details suggest they had reasonable observational experience.
